init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then one day, the wolf knocked on the door of the 92nd little pig.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The 92nd little pig let him in, because he was a polite pig and not the kind of person that would kick someone out in the middle of

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They talked about the weather and their families.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The 92nd little pig told the wolf that he didn't always have this amazing outlook on life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But then, one day, he had a revelation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was determined to make a positive impact on the world, as well.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The 92nd little pig invited the wolf to go with him to the hospital.
